"You're right... This place seems safe, so let's
take a short break."\n<Yukine>\F[7]\AA[F]\FF[24]

(It's strange for us spirits to sweat. Not just
Saku's body, but here the boundary between the
physical and the spiritual becomes
blurred.)\FF[41]\F[4]\AA[F]

(This bath seems clean. If I want to wash off
sweat, this might be a good place.)\F[1]

"Haa haa... It looks like we somehow managed to
escape... But what's going on? This place... it's
incredibly hot. And I'm all sticky from running."\n<Yukine>\F[11]

"It's as hot as the middle of summer here. This
place must really have some strange time or
space."\n<Yukine>\F[8]\AA[F]\FF[23]
"Hang in there a little longer, okay?"\n<Yukine>\F[8]\AA[F]\FF[23]
(I wonder if there's anything useful here...)

(Shampoo and conditioner, plus soap. The shrine
maiden said I should be able to take a bath with
these... I wonder if I can do it right?)\F[5]

(This bath looks clean enough to use... But if I'm
going to take a bath, I need to find some soap.)\F[1]

(It seems like there's a child's spirit outside...
What could it be? They're very thin, and there are
bruises all over their body.)\F[5]

(Even the spirit has wounds remaining, what could
have happened? There shouldn't be any wounds
remaining on a soul.)\F[4]

"There's a child's spirit outside. They seem to
want me to open the door... but that child isn't
coming any closer."\n<Yukine>\F[8]\AA[F]\FF[20]
"...Aren't you going to let them in?"\n<Shuo>\F[8]\AA[FF]\FF[24]
"...What should I do. Maybe I should let them in."\n<Yukine>\F[8]\AA[F]\FF[24]

(It's an old kitchen. It's rusty and there are no

(It's an old stove. There are no signs that it's

(Is this a refrigerator? It's so stiff, I can't

(Is this a refrigerator? There's a big cake with

(There's trash scattered around. A remote control

"Damn... damn... why only me, I did nothing wrong.
That's for sure... damn, can't find my lighter"\n<Male Ghost>

"If he comes in here, he won't get away with it.

"Whoa, what? There's wind blowing inside the
house... why?"\n<Shuo>\F[5]\AA[FF]\FF[28]
"I'll tell you once we go outside..."\n<Yukine>\F[1]\AA[F]\FF[28]
(I wonder if the room has cooled down now.)\n<Yukine>\F[1]\AA[F]\FF[28]
"Tch, it's always such a hassle."\n<Male Ghost>\F[1]\FF[28]\AA[N]

(The tree has been neglected. It's completely
withered, but I wonder if it didn't get any
water.)\F[5]

\F[5]There's a withered tree. Huh... there's something
like a paper stuffed inside the pot.

Been married for four years, and life hasn't
gotten any better. It's all because of the debt my
wife's father made. Just because I became a
guarantor, I'm the only one suffering like this.

The debt collectors came again today. Can't they
see by looking at this house that there's no
money? Of all things, it had to be a loan from a
nasty lender. Damn it, the kid won't stop crying
and it's driving me nuts.

She ran away from home. Dumping that stepchild on
me and vanishing, what a joke. What am I supposed
to do with this kid who doesn't even warm up to
me, not even my own child?

She kept whining "mommy, mommy," so I shut her up
with an ashtray.

They found her. Seems like she committed suicide
somewhere. Her sister wants a funeral, but there's
no money for that.

I was so irritated that I pressed a cigarette burn
onto the kid, felt a bit better after that. Serves
her right.

Those damn debt collectors came again. My head's
gonna explode with this every day... I'll take out
my frustration on that brat. Her body is covered
in purple bruises and it's starting to disgust me,
maybe I'll try strangling her with the TV cord.

The kid's gone blind. Looks like I hit her too
much... Ah, shit, I'm running out of cigarettes,
and the kid's face isn't fit to be seen outside
anymore. Maybe I should just kick her out.

It's so hot I can't go without the air
conditioner. It pisses me off that I have to hit
the outside unit to keep it running... That
useless brat can't do it, so I have to. Got so mad
I kicked her in the face and she passed out with a
nosebleed.
Got blood on my pants, this is the worst.

I threw the kid outside because she was trembling
and annoying. It was too hot to bear without the
air conditioner on, and then her aunt comes
bringing a birthday cake. Telling me to feed it to
the kid, what a joke.

If she endures a day outside, maybe I'll let her
have some cake.

The brat's dead. Just by putting her outside in
August she died. What a weakling, dying on her own
like that. Shit, is this really going to look like
I killed her?

Can't I just make it look like an accident? Come
to think of it, what was that kid's name again?

"This is awful... How could someone do such things
to a child."\n<Yukine>\F[15]
